Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:54.93,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,An endless road ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.31,0:01:59.39,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Two extremities of love and loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:04.10,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Inner demons shrouding the heart—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:07.52,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,they wallow in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:11.31,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Where is my old friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:15.39,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,He is lingering in the shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.85,0:02:22.22,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,convinced that he hasn't veered too far off course, in this world of fleeting destinies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:28.85,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Why do you pine? Why do you yearn?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:33.43,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Nowhere to turn—it's a path of no return.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:37.68,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,The way of life is vicious, we keep going in circles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:39.97,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Hard to discern the truths from the lies,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:42.06,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,tell the evil from the kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:45.56,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,In front of my eyes, a gnarled mess of mountains and waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:50.22,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Why do you tread a path this treacherous?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:54.47,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Embroiled in sinister schemes, in trepidation as the tables turn and turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.93,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,I bid you adieu—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:03:00.64,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,shall we never meet again!
