Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:16.68,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Time has
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:20.77,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,drowned out even the claps of thunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:22.60,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,They scatter
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:26.56,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,the cut-up fragments of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:32.43,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,I can only fumble around, trying to piece them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:36.43,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Why must I climb mountains and peaks
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:38.22,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,to collect
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:42.18,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,the shadows of hanging onto someone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:45.22,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,however late I always seem to be.
Comment: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:45.22,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,*from K: not sure exactly what this line means
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:51.06,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Those places where I once walked,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:55.22,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,what did they
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:59.18,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,look like originally?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.31,0:22:06.89,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Trying to trace those footsteps behind me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.10,0:22:11.06,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,I have forgotten,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.97,0:22:16.35,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,as the path I came from was too far and too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:22.35,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Where will be the end of my journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.72,0:22:26.47,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Where will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.60,0:22:30.35,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Where will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.14,0:22:33.56,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Where will it be...
