Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some things
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.85,0:00:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I must tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Over these years,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.02,0:00:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've forgotten many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My memory
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,has been failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.35,0:00:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.72,0:00:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd forget them if I didn't write them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.14,0:00:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the long-term effect of using such a {\i1}power{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:00:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:00:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're also affected by it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,since you carry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.72,0:01:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a strange energy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,similar to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's our lucky day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't keep an eye out,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd have gotten caught today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,With my skills,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that'd be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Your skills...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What about my skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got quite a haul today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go feast in *Lou Wai Lou later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:58.89,annotation,,0,0,0,,楼外楼 (Lou Wai Lou): an extremely famous traditional restaurant in Hangzhou, China.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:03:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,this looks interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:10.52,Default,On Screen Text,0,0,0,,{\pos(594,886)}(Certificate of Release\N No. 0-0487\NSex: Male, Hometown: Jiangsu)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We even stole from an ex-convict!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is he one of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Those in the same line of work are also often enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.56,0:04:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The net of law has large meshes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but it lets nothing through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Reaching for pockets may thrill you for a minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but it sure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,s-saddens your family for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Young man,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you've learned well in prison,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but reciting slogans
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is pretty much useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,had b-better turn over a new leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wu Mountain House\N(Wu Xie's Antique Shop)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me y-you've forgotten my voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Lao Yang {\i1}(Old Yang){\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You rascal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:05:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard your voice in 3 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.14,0:06:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I can't recognize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound all g-grown up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And you still dare to call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All these years, you never contacted me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you free tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't eaten a decent piece of meat in 3 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Today,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I must have my fill!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,To celebrate your return.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,See you at Lou Wai Lou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Lao Yang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Lao Yang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Lao Wu {\i1}(Old Wu){\i0}, b-bottoms up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You even put on weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In there and out here are like two different worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Count yourself lucky that you could see me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly were you meddling with?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard your cousin's still in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't remind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the one who dragged me into trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He found something precious and just couldn't keep his mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He even confessed to all his past atrocities!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Something precious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite an eerie thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't k-know
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,even if I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We grew up sharing the same clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know my family?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned well from my grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell me its shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past 3 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,your drawing skills haven't improved one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Two branches,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and a stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a pattern?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it look like a tree branch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't say—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it {\i1}is{\i0} a tree branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A bronze tree branch
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,as t-thick as your wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was convinced by my cousin's boasting
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and went deep into the Qinling Mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We trekked for more than a dozen days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Apart from the layers and layers of old-growth forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,we found absolutely nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when we were about to give up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,something different appeared in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The geographical environment in there
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,was very unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was filled with massive banyan trees that could hardly be hugged by even ten men.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In that forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,tree roots crawled all over the forest floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and you couldn't walk normally at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stone figures?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,As the saying goes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,where bamboo doesn't survive the land's saline,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,where bridges of offerings sprout overnight;
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,where mountains look all brown and dry,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,it is worth panning the sand and soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In such places with abnormal vegetation growth,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,something has to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So we followed the leads of the stone men
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and continued to venture deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,As we walked,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,an ancient path appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Once inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,we walked for hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The deeper we delved, the thicker the aerial roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that structure
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,was like a pyramid planted upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Stairs were carved
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,on all four slopes in the pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There were over a hundred steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time we reached the bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,it was already midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it wasn't an ancient tomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was more like
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,a sacrificial altar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The mud well in the center
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,was around a dozen meters deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.02,0:11:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When we pointed our flashlights inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,we saw nothing but grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,As for what was in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you can guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If it really was a sacrificial altar,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,there must have been a sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There must have been something beneath the altar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I silently recited every possible thing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I could think of,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but it turned out
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to be way more shocking
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that I had expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My cousin and I took turns digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:11:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,15 meters in,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:11:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,still no sign of the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could have known how deep that thing was?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end of the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,apart from some broken jade tiles and earthenware,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,there was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of us were beyond exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,According to my cousin,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd already seen some interesting things,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so we might as well leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,however,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't swallow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I had been taken over,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to keep digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a strong feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that there must be
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,a secret hidden underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.56,0:12:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it was as if it came from hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It was chilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it really bronzeware?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Exactly like what I drew for you just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pity, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.72,0:13:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We did a rough calculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The part of the bronze tree branch that was buried underground
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,must have gone on for about 10 more meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing must at least have been 30 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that gigantic
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,must have required more than ten thousand men to build.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep spinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How could there be a vessel that huge?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you're too inexperienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you took nothing, then why were you in jail for 3 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I didn't exactly take {\i1}nothing{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.10,0:14:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,where did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm gonna get mad if you keep on pinching!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't go easy on me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no need to react like that even if you saw something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Spill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Bet you've never seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be green with envy once you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I took it from a zombie
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in the sacrificial pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A zombie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It turned up by accident
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,when I was digging that pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:15:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That zombie was tied up tightly by rattan ropes, like a cocoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was probably
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,a human sacrifice of relatively high status.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,was on that zombie's earlobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I took it since I thought it looked good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Green tinged with black.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be a first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that expression?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so uptight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me there's something more to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really getting jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.97,0:15:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen it somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The hexagonal bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,T-T-This thing is really so peculiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it in the Seven-Star Palace and the undersea tomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite a bizarre bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it rings,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,it hypnotizes anyone who hears it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Although,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you look fine wearing it on your ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought the sacrificial altar was enough for me to boast for a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to your adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,mine are absolutely pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you like it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder you're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's filled with rosin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't ring anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, ordinary people
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,should keep their distance from that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But {\i1}you{\i0} are not an ordinary guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't I know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more curious than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're interested,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,let's visit that place again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a mark there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There might be more of these bells.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You learned nothing in jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Reoffending warrants a harsher sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You might even get executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.77,0:17:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that one-track mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell me if you're low on cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can give it to you, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When we were young, you'd ask for interest over even a popsicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You still remember? That was so long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens in childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,can affect someone throughout their whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not entirely blameless for how I am today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I never told you to rob graves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it my fault when you were the one who decided to go astray?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You were indeed part of the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You used to always tell me stories about your grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You even flaunted his treasures to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.27,0:18:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I was tempted back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,if I had the chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I must go on an adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that would make my life worthwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly speaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,in the past 3 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've thought of that place every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't take it lying down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pull that on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That cousin of yours never heard my stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You can cut the melancholic act.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even act a little melancholic now that we're at the West Lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're heartless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:18:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just curious and want to see it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Second,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:03.72,annotation,,0,0,0,,*Uncle Three: Wu Xie's third uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't you say your *Uncle Three went missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Since there were the same bells,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,some fresh clues might show up over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Since there were the same bells,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,some fresh clues might show up over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:18.02,annotation,,0,0,0,,T/N: from the second volume of the novel, {\i1}Angry Sea, Hidden Sands{\i0}. As Chinese can be read from both left to right and right to left, the message was meant to be intentionally confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:18.02,Default,不需要后期,0,0,0,,(Wu Sanxing)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:14.72,Default,不需要后期,0,0,0,,(caused me)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:15.22,Default,不需要后期,0,0,0,,(caused me to die a horrible death)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:18.02,Default,不需要后期,0,0,0,,(Xie Lianhuan)\N(caused me to die a horrible death)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Lao Wu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you count yourself as my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who said you wanted to find your Uncle Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,w-what's the big deal making the trip with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I harm you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you know some feng shui, y-y-you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll say this first:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not allowed to take anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Also,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,give me that bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Still putting on that tough act?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(956,148)}I bet you wanted to go from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:19:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(956,148)}Lao Wu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.81,0:19:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(956,148)}You'd better honor your word!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:19:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.93,0:19:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! A p-p-plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Say,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't we have just taken a flight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The road was so bumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been out for just a few days, and you're already running around with a big backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you got checked?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,With your looks, they'll recognize you from a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't deny that.
